  "title": "BEAUTICIAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p><p>· Performing various skin treatments according to clients’ needs, such as facial/skin treatments.</p><p>· Scheduling client’s appointments</p><p>· Data entry of client's information</p><p>· Keep documentation and maintain client’s files</p><p>· Perform pre-treatment and after treatment consultation</p><p>· Acknowledge and respond to relevant client’s queries, needs and expectations</p><p>· Suggest and promote retail products or additional services</p><p>· Stock taking</p><p>· Ensure treatment rooms are clean and neat</p><p>· Any other administrative task when required</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Good communications and interpersonal skills</p><p>· Well-groomed</p><p>· Positive attitude and good team player</p><p>· Excellent interpersonal skills, time management and organization skills</p><p>· Sale oriented, service oriented and customer focused</p><p>· Able to work shifts, weekends and Public Holidays</p>",
